title: 209 - Keto Killer
description:
Sustain. To support, hold up, bear from below. Everyone talks a LOT about becoming successful and reaching goals. But what does it take to sustain it? On today’s podcast, CJ asks Jemal, ET, Josh, and Karl how they’ve been able to not only sustain their success but how they’ve been able to increase it. The mental toughness, the importance of keeping the vision alive, and how to keep believing if you’re in a position where you haven’t yet reached success. It’s all talked about on today’s podcast and it’s the perfect conversation to start the year. 
 The Secret to Success Topics:
  [04:29] - Fair or Foul
 [15:00] - Sustain 
 [24:14] - Healthy Fear
 [40:42] - Growth
 [1:02:00] - Crazy Faith

  Organifi is giving our listeners 20% off of their order just go to www.organifi.com/success. Their superfood green juice powder allows you to get your greens anytime anywhere while on the go.
 Get fresh pre-measured ingredients delivered straight to your door. Hello Fresh is our choice for meal planning for ourselves and our families. For a limited time get 9 FREE meals by visiting www.hellofresh.com/success9 and use the promo code “SUCCESS9”

  Secrets of the 1%:
  If you always try to get better you can’t catch that.
 Have an insatiable desire to be better.
